                                <item xml:id="e1">
                                    <desc>The name of the first owner seems to have been <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11817WaldaHanna">Walda Ḥannā</persName>,
                                        for which those of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11818Yohannes">Yoḥannǝs Walda Yoḥannǝs</persName> and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11819Zamaryam">Zamāryām</persName> have been substituted.
                                    </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a1">
                                    <locus target="#2r"/>
                                    <desc type="Unclear">Prayer in the handwriting of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11819Zamaryam">Zamāryām</persName>
                           </desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <locus target="#2r"/>
                                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">The note, which is written over <ref target="#a1"/>, states that the manuscript belongs to the church of 
